    "en": {
      "title": "The President went from Katunayake Air Force Base - in an Antonov plane",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Katunayake airport sources stated that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has left Sri Lanka for Maldives this morning (13th).",
        "The President, his wife and one of their security officers have left. They left the Katunayake Air Force Base for Maldives at around 01.45 this morning in an Antonov-32 (AN-32) aircraft belonging to the Sri Lanka Air Force."
      ],
